矽速科技（Sipeed）与PLCT实验室联合宣布，RuyiSDK 将作为 Lic.message: Sipeed and the PLCT Lab jointly announced that RuyiSDK will serve as the upstream support platform for the LicheePi 4A development board, taking responsibility for future system maintenance, upgrades, and software support. This not only promotes the development and broader adoption of RISC-V development boards but also provides developers with a more convenient and efficient development environment.

一个专门用来开发能够运行在 RISC-V 架构设备上的软件和应用的工具箱。可以帮.message: A toolbox specifically designed for developing software and applications that can run on RISC-V architecture devices. It can help developers write and test their own programs without the need for users to spend time setting up the environment.

RuyiSDK 开发者社区现已开启.message: The RuyiSDK Community has a new discussion forum—join the conversation!

社区提供文档和教程、论坛和技术讨论区等功能，目的是为 RISC-V 开发者提供一.message: The community provides functions such as documentation and tutorials, forums and technical discussion areas, with the aim of providing an open communication platform for RISC-V developers, providing mutual technical support and resource sharing, gathering RISC-V developers and promoting the development of the RISC-V ecosystem.

我们的代码完全开源，意味着每个人都可以在许可证允许的条件下查看、使用、修改和共享.message: Our code is completely open source, which means everyone can view, use, modify and share it under the conditions permitted by the license. Whether you are a developer, student, enthusiast or enterprise, you can freely participate in our project and build a better RuyiSDK together. Welcome to join our community and promote the development of open source together!

玄铁携手 PLCT 实验室推出 RISC-V 系列课程，包含三大中级课程与两大高.message: XuanTie and the PLCT Lab jointly launched a series of RISC-V courses, including three intermediate courses and two advanced advanced courses. Taught by a team of professional instructors, covering areas such as RISC-V software ecosystem and compiler development. Provides opportunities for practical experience on mainstream development boards, and after graduation, can participate in technical salons, Hackathon competitions, and other activities, communicate with industry experts, and obtain career development opportunities.

PLCT实验室携香山南湖笔记本倾情参与BOSC世界RISC-V日.message: PLCT Lab Participates in BOSC World RISC-V Day with Xiangshan Nanhu Laptop

2025年8月8日，World RISC-V Days 北京站在北京开源芯片研究.message: On August 8, 2025, World RISC-V Days Beijing Station was successfully held at the Beijing Open Source Chip Research Institute. As the first World RISC-V Day celebration launched by the RISC-V International Foundation, this event brought together industry experts, enterprise representatives and developers from various regions to share insights and exchange cooperation, further promoting the widespread adoption and continuous innovation of RISC-V in China and globally.

人物｜程龙灿：做RISC-V世界的 “连接者”.message: Profile | Chenglong Can: Being a 'Connector' in the RISC-V World

程龙灿，PLCT实验室运营经理，从测试小队成员转型为社区运营专家。他带着对Lin.message: Chenglong Can, Operations Manager at PLCT Lab, transformed from a testing team member to a community operations expert. With his passion for Linux and technical background, he is committed to making RISC-V technology visible to more people and promoting orderly community development. As a 'connector' in the RISC-V world, he builds bridges between technology and users, allowing the value of the open source ecosystem to be fully realized.
